Maybe you\'92re already familiar with all of this. Maybe you have access to a bunch of different human's accounts. Maybe you\'92re an expert archeologist from an alien race, digging through the remains of the last part of the anthropocene. Maybe it\'92s more interesting to talk about less rational things. Things more unique to me but maybe somehow also more universally human (this is the kind of thing that some people try to teach you if pursue a career in art).\
